    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行行长内田缓解利率担忧后，日本股市飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/japan-s-stock-futures-signal-lower-open-as-market-stays-on-edge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行副行长内田新一表示，在市场不稳定时央行不会加息，导致日元走弱，日本股市飙升，扭转了早前的跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/japan-s-stock-futures-signal-lower-open-as-market-stays-on-edge</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 23:35:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
